Package: CDCdata
Title: Access CDC Open Data Portal Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Patrick","Rekieta",email = "Patrick.Rekieta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-4446-9665"))
  )
Description: Provides a modern R interface to the CDC's open data portal (data.cdc.gov). 
  Supports dataset discovery, flexible querying with SoQL, pagination, rate limiting, and 
  optional authentication via app tokens. This is an independent open-source project and is not 
  affiliated with, endorsed by, or representative of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention 
  (CDC) or the U.S. Government.
